dct_description_sm: "The Russian River Watershed GIS project is intended to compile a set of standardized, spatial data in support of recovery planning for three threatened salmonid species in the Russian River basin - steelhead trout, chinook and coho salmon."--publisher's website.
a joint project of NOAA Fisheries & Circuit Rider Productions, Inc.
System requirements: ESRI ArcView or ArcExplorer (included); web browser.
